			<div class="comment-content">
				<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://www.gimmesomeoven.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
My university cafeteria had a peanut butter pie so I made it for my friends who went there. They all told  me it reminded me of the good old days, which was over 10 years ago. The crust was amazing. Thank you for impressing my friends.</p>
